AddressTypeAheadServlet - Class in com.ansi.scilla.web.address.servlet
This url searches the following address table fields for the search type ahead "term": name address 1 address 2 city zip and returns the following fields: id = address_id label = name:address 1:address 2:city:state:zip value = name The url for delete will return methodNotAllowed The url for post will return methodNotAllowed The url for get will be one of: /addressSearch?term= (returns null list) /addressSearch?term=<searchTerm> (returns all records containing <searchTerm>) The servlet will return 404 Not Found if there is no "term=" found.
